                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5084" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0731</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9054 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化雨润物细无声，一枝一叶总关情——胖东来服务利润链如何创造业界神奇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Turn rain and moisten things silently, one branch and one leaf always close feelings ——How does fat east serve the profit chain to create the magic of the industry</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李唯滨，吴婧娴</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">哈尔滨商业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">胖东来商贸集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">胖东来；服务利润链；企业文化；价值创造</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Fat Donglai; service profit chain; corporate culture; value creation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在中国的零售行业，一个河南省三线城市的超市——胖东来，因1998年的一场大火而化为灰烬被人知晓，又因在2020年新型冠状肺炎疫情期间捐资五千万和“所有蔬菜按进价销售”而受社会关注。这家创立于1995年的40平米小商店，发展成为当今在许昌、新乡等城市拥有30多家连锁分店、近万名员工的独霸许昌、新乡市场的连锁超市，在整个百货商超连锁行业拥有无可比拟的客户口碑以及市场知名度，接连打败丹尼斯、沃尔玛等大型商超，被誉为中国超市界的传奇神店、零售行业的标杆。本案例从服务利润链的视角分析胖东来成功的原因，通过对胖东来优质服务和薪酬激励机制的探讨，明确了胖东来的服务利润链对企业价值创造的促进作用，揭示了胖东来的成功之道是靠着丰厚的薪酬和激励机制保证的优质服务构成的服务利润链所形成的核心竞争能力。研究表明以员工满意度与忠诚度、员工为顾客提供的服务价值、顾客满意度与忠诚度以及企业价值创造所形成的一条循环作用的闭合链——服务利润链是创造胖东来业界神奇的重要推动力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In China&#39;s retail industry, fat Dong Lai, a supermarket in the third tier city of Henan Province, was known to be ashes due to a fire in 1998, and received social attention for donating 50 million yuan and &quot;selling all vegetables at the input price&quot; during the new coronary pneumonia epidemic in 2020. Founded in 1995, this 40 square meter small store has developed into a chain supermarket with more than 30 chain stores and nearly 10000 employees in Xuchang, Xinxiang and other cities. It has unparalleled customer reputation and market awareness in the whole department store super chain industry. It has successively defeated Dennis, Wal Mart and other large-scale super businesses, and is known as the Chinese supermarket industry The benchmark of legendary stores and retail industry. The research shows that the service profit chain is an important driving force to create the industry magic of fat Dong, which is a closed chain formed by employee satisfaction and loyalty, employee service value for customers, customer satisfaction and loyalty, and enterprise value creation. From the perspective of service profit chain, this case analyzes the reasons for the success of fat Dong Lai. Through the discussion of its high-quality service and salary incentive mechanism, it makes clear that the service profit chain of fat Dong Lai promotes the value creation of enterprises, and reveals that the way to success of fat Dong Lai is the core competition formed by the service profit chain composed of high-quality services guaranteed by rich salary and incentive mechanism Ability.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业管理》、《高级管理会计理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务利润链的管理策略以及实现企业价值创造</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-01</td>
                            </tr>
